snippet.title: Children’s Pocket Money Comes in Handy after Demonetisation of Rs 500, 1000 Notes

localized.description:
Uttar Pradesh: Children’s pocket money comes in handy after demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes. Peoples are queued up outside ATMs and banks to exchange their old notes.
